  "task_html": "<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UAHEbxz4Ydw&list=PLCwTOdPGQsAyGFOl88eq6XEUYeof5JAh-&index=3\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"video-link-card\" style=\"margin-bottom:16px;\">\n  <div class=\"video-link-icon\">▶</div>\n  <div class=\"video-link-text\">\n    <div class=\"video-link-title\">Längenmaße umrechnen</div>\n    <div class=\"video-link-sub\">YouTube: Einfach erklärt · Rechnen mit Größen</div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"video-link-arrow\">↗</div>\n</a>\n<p style=\"font-size:14px;margin:0 0 14px 0;\"><strong>Ergänze die fehlenden Werte in der Tabelle.</strong></p>\n\n<div class=\"task-block task-blue\">\n  <div class=\"task-block-label\">Längenmaße</div>\n  <div class=\"tbl-wrap\"><table>\n    <thead><tr><th>mm</th><th>cm</th><th>dm</th><th>m</th><th>km</th></tr></thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td class=\"given\">85 mm</td>\n        <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"8.5\" placeholder=\"?\"></td>\n        <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"0.85\" placeholder=\"?\"></td>\n        <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"0.085\" placeholder=\"?\"></td>\n        <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"0.000085\" placeholder=\"?\"></td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"2300\" placeholder=\"?\"></td>\n        <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"230\" placeholder=\"?\"></td>\n        <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"23\" placeholder=\"?\"></td>\n        <td class=\"given\">2,3 m</td>\n        <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"0.0023\" placeholder=\"?\"></td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"check-bar\">\n  <button class=\"btn-check\" onclick=\"checkEinheiten()\">✓ Überprüfen</button>\n  <button class=\"btn-reset\" onclick=\"resetEinheiten()\">↺ Zurücksetzen</button>\n  <span class=\"check-result\" id=\"check-result-einheiten\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"task-block task-orange\" style=\"margin-top:14px;\">\n  <div class=\"task-block-label\">✏️ Erkläre</div>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:8px;\">Erkläre: Warum hat die Umrechnung von cm → m den Faktor 1/100 (also ÷100)? Was bedeutet das anschaulich?</p>\n  <textarea style=\"width:100%;min-height:70px;padding:8px 10px;border:1.5px solid #fed7aa;border-radius:8px;font-size:13px;font-family:inherit;resize:vertical;\" placeholder=\"Deine Erklärung...\"></textarea>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:var(--ink2);margin-top:6px;\">💡 Denke daran: 1 m = 100 cm. Wenn du von einer kleineren in eine größere Einheit umrechnest, wird die Zahl kleiner.</p>\n</div>",
  "sol_html": "<div class=\"h2-example\" style=\"margin:0;\"><div class=\"h2-example-title\">Lösung</div><div class=\"h2-example-calc\">\n<div class=\"tbl-wrap\"><table>\n  <thead><tr><th>mm</th><th>cm</th><th>dm</th><th>m</th><th>km</th></tr></thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr><td class=\"given\">85</td><td>8,5</td><td>0,85</td><td>0,085</td><td>0,000085</td></tr>\n    <tr><td>2 300</td><td>230</td><td>23</td><td class=\"given\">2,3</td><td>0,0023</td></tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table></div>\n<p style=\"font-size:13px;margin-top:10px;\">Jede Stufe nach rechts: ÷10 &nbsp;|&nbsp; Jede Stufe nach links: ×10</p>\n</div></div>"
}